    public class XmlNamedModelledBinaryInteractionWriter
extends XmlModelledBinaryInteractionWriter
    Compact XML 2.5 writer for a modelled binary interaction (ignore experimental details) which have a fullname and aliases in addition to the shortname. It will write cooperative effects as attributes
